  version: {{ version }}

  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

    - msrest >=0.5.0
    - msrestazure >=0.4.32,<2.0.0
    - azure-common >=1.1,<2.0
